<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>New Payment Transaction - WealthWise</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: "Segoe UI", Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background-color: #eef2f7;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 30px;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 650px;
      background: #ffffff;
      padding: 25px 30px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 6px 14px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
      margin: auto;
      border-top: 5px solid #0056b3;
    }
    h2 {
      color: #0056b3;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      font-size: 22px;
    }
    p {
      color: #444;
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin: 8px 0;
    }
    .highlight {
      color: #0056b3;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .amount {
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #e53935; /* Red for amount */
    }
    .btn {
       display: inline-block;
        padding: 12px 22px;
        margin: 25px 0;
        background-color: #e4e3e3; /* --nav-btns-bg */
        color: #1e3a8a; /* --nav-btns-text */
        text-decoration: none;
        font-size: 16px;
        font-weight: bold;
        border-radius: 6px;
    }
    .btn:hover {
        background-color: rgb(234, 236, 241); /* --nav-btns-bg-hover */
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 25px;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #777;
      border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
      padding-top: 12px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h2>New Payment Transaction</h2>
    <p>Hello <span class="highlight">WealthWise Admin</span>,</p>
    
    <p>A new transaction has been created by <strong>{{name}}</strong>.</p>
    <p>Transaction Amount: <span class="amount">${{amount}}</span></p>
    
    <p>You can view the full details of this transaction by clicking the button below:</p>
    <p><a class="btn" href="{{link}}">View Transaction Details</a></p>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p>Best regards,<br>ðŸ’¼ WealthWise Transactions Team</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
